name: SportsHeadline
0: ”Alexa ask Sports Headline to get me a headline”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: sports headline
des:
This skill allows the user to ask for a sports headline. Once a headline has been obtained Alexa will read it out.
For another headline, say "get me a headline".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
